description: A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul,like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone,and feel the charm of existence was created for the bliss of souls like mine.I am so happy,my dear friend,so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence,that I neglect my talents
